      Constructs a new Application with default status as PENDING and today's date.

      flatType - The type of flat applied for (e.g., 2-Room, 3-Room).

      flatType - The flat type applied for.
      applicant - The applicant.
      status - The application status.
      date - The date of application.
      bookingRequested - Whether the applicant has requested a booking.
      withdrawalRequested - Whether the applicant has requested a withdrawal.
